title: 01/28: Stefon Diggs and Jerome Bettis Interviews; Free Agency Preview (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Live from radio row, welcome to Super Bowl week! Stefon Diggs and Jerome Bettis join the show. Bettis talks about Derrick Henry among other things and what kind of workload he expects for Henry next season. Meanwhile, Diggs discusses sharing targets with Adam Thielen, his thoughts on his new Offensive Coordinator and much more. Plus we preview free agency as Philip Rivers, Tom Brady and Hunter Henry are among the headliners.
